stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> PlanParsed : runPlan(plan)
    PlanParsed --> GateSynthesis : pre-flight
    GateSynthesis --> SliceReady : advisory printed (L6)
    SliceReady --> BuildPrompt
    BuildPrompt --> AutoSkillLookup : retrieve matching skills (L2)
    AutoSkillLookup --> WorkerInvoke : inject skill context + trajectory sentinel
    WorkerInvoke --> GateRun
    GateRun --> GatePassed : exit 0
    GateRun --> ReflexionBuild : exit != 0 (L7)
    ReflexionBuild --> BuildPrompt : retry with reflexion block
    GatePassed --> TrajectoryWrite : extract sentinel-wrapped note (L8)
    TrajectoryWrite --> AutoSkillCapture : save slice pattern (L2)
    AutoSkillCapture --> ReviewerCheck : brain.gate-check
    ReviewerCheck --> ReviewerInvoke : runtime.reviewer.enabled (L4, opt-in)
    ReviewerCheck --> NextSlice : reviewer disabled
    ReviewerInvoke --> NextSlice : advisory verdict (D6)
    ReviewerInvoke --> BlockedCritical : critical + blockOnCritical=true
    BlockedCritical --> [*]
    NextSlice --> SliceReady : more slices
    NextSlice --> RunComplete : last slice
    RunComplete --> PostmortemWrite : retries, gateFlaps, costDelta, driftDelta (L5)
    PostmortemWrite --> FederationPublish : brain.federation.enabled (L4-lite)
    FederationPublish --> [*]
    PostmortemWrite --> [*]
